product.title: Lambert - The Elie Vegan Leather Bag in Black
product.body_html: Not you average purse. Made with high-end, PETA-certified vegan leather, this premium bag features integrated compartments and can easily be worn in 3 different ways by adjusting the straps: as a handbag, a shoulder bag, or a backpack. 29cm (length) x 25cm (height) x 12,5cm (width).
